{"tid":2458160,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"經典喜劇《神探飛機頭》拍第3集 占基利有望回歸","createTime":"2021-03-23T08:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T11:52:58.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d38b947c2e47307842311b8540cd21a3cc323fc","tid":2458160,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:22:42.000Z","msg":"於90年代因誇張表情而爆紅的「扮嘢王」占基利（Jim Carrey），有望回歸經典笑片《神探飛機頭》（Ace Ventura）系列。電影公司最近就宣佈將會開拍第3集，令粉絲非常興奮。<br />\n<br />\n《神探飛機頭》系列之製作公司Morgan Creek Entertainment表示：「我們很興奮，有300萬粉絲都在《神探飛機頭》Facebook官網談論，很想有第3集。」他們又指，因為大家都留在家中，特別喜歡看這經典的電影，又很想戲中的經典人物回歸，因此已與Amazon傾好開拍第3集，並由《超音鼠大電影》（Sonic the Hedgehog）編劇負責執筆。然而，占基利的回歸仍有待落實。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210321/XXF3TEBSGRGSPOJZG6YYR5KKFA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210321%2FXXF3TEBSGRGSPOJZG6YYR5KKFA%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97WAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=4396dc8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210321%2FXXF3TEBSGRGSPOJZG6YYR5KKFA%2F&h=12f0290d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210321/XXF3TEBSGRGSPOJZG6YYR5KKFA/</a>"},{"pid":"48f8207689061e0accc0377126cec61e6bc14419","tid":2458160,"uid":165361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BF16eA7sdqo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBF16eA7sdqo&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97WAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=8b3545d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BF16eA7sdqo</a>"},{"pid":"e857ae314a604f807e81c050bf67289d454cd9a5","tid":2458160,"uid":126044,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"依家占基利D戲都比較難笑得出<br />\n<br />\n個樣好憔悴<br />\n又抑鬱症又俾前度屈佢有性病"},{"pid":"1b24f7c524a2b34a134f899f5732751e9dea4a49","tid":2458160,"uid":278118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"